CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 18, 1959, pg. A10, reads: "Celebrates 16th Birthday - Barbara Elaine Williams, 7211 Mount Vernon St., celebrated her birthday with a gala party Friday evening. On the guest list were Diane Dixon, Beverly Wall, Beverly Malone, Jacqueline Baglay, Judith Hopson, Jo Anne Cobb, Earlene Palmer, William Short, Ronald Southall, Janice Peyton, Raymond Dennis, Joyce Chandler, Fern Harper, Vernetta Thompson, Alleen Bullock, Andrew Dixon, Chester Hopson, Clarence Walker, Henry Peyton, Marvin Wesley, Harvey Mahone, Arnold Smith, John Thomas, William Robinson, William Malloy, Lois Haakins, Paul Anderson, Larry Malone, Gloria Morgan, John (Herky) Tipton, Charles Baines, Robert Best, James Roberts, John Woodson and Martin Jones. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Barbara Elaine Williams lighting candles on sixteenth birthday cake, surrounded by Diane Dixon, Beverly Wall, Beverly Malone, Jacqueline Baglay, Judith Hopson, Jo Anne Cobb, Earlene Palmer, William Short, Ronald Southall, Janice Peyton, Raymond Dennis, Joyce Chandler, Fern Harper, Vernetta Thompson, Alleen Bullock, Andrew Dixon, Chester Hopson, Clarence Walker, Henry Peyton, Marvin Wesley, Harvey Mahone, Arnold Smith, John Thomas, William Robinson, William Malloy, Lois Haakins, Paul Anderson, Larry Malone, Gloria Morgan, John "Herky" Tipton, Charles Baines, Robert Best, James Roberts, John Woodson, and Martin Jones for party in Williams home, 7211 Mount Vernon Street
